name: I Flew Lynx Air's INAUGURAL FLIGHT!
description:
Lynx Air is Canada's newest "ultra-affordable" airline, and they officially launched flights on April 7th, 2022, with a fleet of Boeing 737 MAX 8s!

See what the Lynx Air experience was like on board their inaugural flight from Calgary to Vancouver!

With many thanks to Will Ross-Dushinski for the thumbnail photo: https://www.instagram.com/willrdaviation
